From the following data:
Prices: {}
Ratings: {}

Extract the rating and price range for the hotel named ```json
{
  "tool": "query_llm",
  "args": {
    "prompt": "Based on the following data:\nPrices: <Prices/>\nRatings: <Ratings/>\n\nFind the hotel that meets these criteria:\n1. It is NOT 'London Luxury Hotel'.\n2. Its price is 160 or less.\n3. Among those that fit the budget, it has the highest rating.\n\nReturn only the name of this hotel."
  }
}
```. 
Return the result in the format: "Rating: [rating], Price Range: [price range]".
